Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), dh-systemd (>= 1.5), lsb-release
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: http://www.open-xchange.com

Package: open-xchange
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, init-system-helpers, open-xchange-hazelcast, open-xchange-authentication, open-xchange-authorization, open-xchange-mailstore, open-xchange-smtp (>= @OXVERSION@), open-xchange-grizzly | open-xchange-httpservice
Description: The Open-Xchange backend
 This package provides the dependencies to install a working Open-Xchange backend system. By installing this package a minimal backend is
 installed. Additionally this package provides the init script for starting the backend on system boot.
